    "The Dutch Research Council asks investigators for their 10 most relevant outputs, including papers, software, databases, and patents.",
    "The National Science Foundation in the United States similarly limits the number of publications listed on investigators' biographical sketches to five products most closely related to the proposed project and five other significant products.",
